{"id":11248,"date":"2013-01-09T11:39:56","date_gmt":"2013-01-09T16:39:56","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=11248"},"modified":"2019-04-17T16:21:28","modified_gmt":"2019-04-17T12:21:28","slug":"believers-paradise-admire-above-them","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/09\/believers-paradise-admire-above-them\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Paradise: Believers in Paradise admire those above them"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<b>Verily, the people of Paradise will look upon the inhabitants of mansions above them, just as they look at a brilliant star on the horizon in the East or West, due to their favor over them.<\/b>\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, are these the dwellings of the prophets whom no one else can reach?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>No. By the One in whose hand is my soul, they are men who had faith in Allah and believed in the messengers<\/b>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 3083, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2831<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<b><i>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/i><\/b>\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e <strong>\u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0647\u0652\u0644